Package: updateR
Maintainer: Mark Cowley <m.cowley@garvan.org.au>
License: GPL-2
Title: Package development toolkit
Type: Package
Author: Mark Cowley <m.cowley@garvan.org.au>
Description: A collection of functions that enable R
    package maintainers to build and update packages. A
    shell script essentially runs roxygen, R CMD CHECK &
    BUILD & INSTALL. Tools for refreshing a currently
    loaded library are included, as well as finding the
    dependencies of any function.
Version: 1.0.4
URL: http://pwbc.garvan.unsw.edu.au
Date: 2011-09-21
Depends:
    R (>= 2.12.0),
    codetools
Suggests:
    Rd2roxygen
Collate:
    'available.packages.bioc.R'
    'edit.func.R'
    'find.src.file.R'
    'get.full.path.R'
    'get.function.dependencies.R'
    'import.function.R'
    'is.dir.R'
    'list.my.packages.R'
    'mjc2roxygen.R'
    'relibrary.R'
    'trim.R'
    'unlibrary.R'
    'updateR-package.R'
    'updateR.R'
    'which.package.R'
